snippet: Texas’ 83rd legislative session will feature fewer women and more ethnic diversity than in the past, and two-thirds of the lawmakers are either lawyers or business executives.

byline.contributor:
Julián Aguilar and Becca 
Aaronson contributed reporting.

lead_paragraph: Texas’ 83rd legislative session will feature fewer women and more ethnic diversity than in the past, and two-thirds of the lawmakers are either lawyers or business executives.

headline.seo: Some Demographic Shifts in Texas’ New Legislature
headline.main: In the New Legislature, Some Demographic Shifts
headline.print_headline: In the New Legislature, Some Demographic Shifts
